    </span>
</div>
<div class="enlarge_measure">
    <div class="img_wrap">
        <img data-original="https://media.npr.org/assets/img/2019/12/19/gettyimages-1158941986_slide-2abb14d9690deef9a7fb3b9c7e8dc87c4e990aee-s1200.jpg" alt="" />
    </div>
