<div class="enlarge_html">
    <div class="image_data">
        <p class="caption">A replica of a North Korean missile and South Korean surface-to-air missiles stands at the Korean War Memorial in Seoul, South Korea. North Korea fired unidentified short-range projectiles during a test in August, a move that displeased U.S. negotiators.</p>
        <span class="credit" aria-label="Image credit">
            
